+/*!
+ * \brief Load NVFP4 KV scale-factors for one CTA tile (contiguous/ragged layout).
+ *
+ * Contiguous analog of page_produce_kv_sf — no page indirection.
+ * kv_abs_base is the absolute first token index for this CTA tile
